Dialogues.Speaker: Maji
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: We're temporarily suspending all trial runs for today, {PlayerName}. We need to do some maintenance on "Lollo Navigator"!

Dialogues.Speaker: Maji
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: Well... in a way, yes, but it's only temporary. We need to recalibrate the dynamic map info of "Lollo Navigator" after its long trial run.

Dialogues.Speaker: Maji
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: No, no, no. We just need to recalibrate the dynamic map info of "Lollo Navigator" after its long trial run.

Dialogues.Speaker: Maji
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: We need to ensure everything's accurate and on time. Now that you're here, why not help me find a few things as references for the information?

Dialogues.Speaker: Maji
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: You know, besides road conditions, things like plants, animals, minerals, their growth cycles, and their environments are also key references for dynamic information.

Dialogues.Speaker: Maji
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: The objects I need are sent to your Terminal. Good luck out there!

Dialogues.Speaker: Maji
Dialogues.PlotLineKey: Really appreciate the hard work. These reference objects will definitely come in handy. Here's your pay for today, you earned it.
